    <title>vue-cli构建项目</title>
    <link href="https://lguoliang.github.io/Blogs/2018/05/15/vue-cli%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/"/>
    <id>https://lguoliang.github.io/Blogs/2018/05/15/vue-cli构建项目/</id>
    <published>2018-05-15T08:04:35.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-05-17T06:49:08.039Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>简单记录一下vue-cli构建项目，真的简单记录。</p><h2 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 全局安装 vue-cli</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install --global vue-cli</span><br><span class="line"># 创建一个基于 webpack 模板的新项目</span><br><span class="line">$ vue init webpack my-project</span><br><span class="line"># 安装依赖，走你</span><br><span class="line">$ cd my-project</span><br><span class="line">$ npm run dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><h3 id="初始化选项如下-最后按回车use-NPM就可以啦"><a href="#初始化选项如下-最后按回车use-NPM就可以啦" class="headerlink" title="初始化选项如下,最后按回车use NPM就可以啦"></a>初始化选项如下,最后按回车use NPM就可以啦</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ vue init webpack vue-project</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  A newer version of vue-cli is available.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  latest:    2.9.3</span><br><span class="line">  installed: 2.9.1</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">? Project name (vue-project)  // 项目名称</span><br><span class="line">? Project name vue-project</span><br><span class="line">? Project description (A Vue.js project)  // 项目描述</span><br><span class="line">? Project description A Vue.js project</span><br><span class="line">? Author (GL &lt;873928073@qq.com&gt;)  // 作者</span><br><span class="line">? Author GL &lt;873928073@qq.com&gt;</span><br><span class="line">? Vue build (Use arrow keys)  // 是否安装编译器</span><br><span class="line">? Vue build standalone</span><br><span class="line">? Install vue-router? (Y/n) // 是否安装 vue-router（路由）</span><br><span class="line">? Install vue-router? Yes</span><br><span class="line">? Use ESLint to lint your code? (Y/n) // 是否需要使用 ESLint 来检查你的代码</span><br><span class="line">? Use ESLint to lint your code? Yes</span><br><span class="line">? Pick an ESLint preset (Use arrow keys)</span><br><span class="line">? Pick an ESLint preset Standard</span><br><span class="line">? Set up unit tests (Y/n) n // 是否需要安装测试功能。</span><br><span class="line">? Set up unit tests No</span><br><span class="line">? Setup e2e tests with Nightwatch? (Y/n) n</span><br><span class="line">? Setup e2e tests with Nightwatch? No</span><br><span class="line">? Should we run `npm install` for you after the project has been created? (reco</span><br><span class="line">mmended) (Use arrow keys)</span><br><span class="line">&gt; Yes, use NPM</span><br><span class="line">  Yes, use Yarn</span><br><span class="line">  No, I will handle that myself</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://note.youdao.com/yws/public/resource/7f17893a71ff4c65a2eeb1b02d8e9e39/xmlnote/WEBRESOURCE525db9b82a81be11842301ac0a8bf683/576" alt="vue-cli"></p><h3 id="初始完后执行-npm-run-dev-命令，在浏览器里面打开页面显示如下，这样项目就创建完成了。"><a href="#初始完后执行-npm-run-dev-命令，在浏览器里面打开页面显示如下，这样项目就创建完成了。" class="headerlink" title="初始完后执行 npm run dev 命令，在浏览器里面打开页面显示如下，这样项目就创建完成了。"></a>初始完后执行 npm run dev 命令，在浏览器里面打开页面显示如下，这样项目就创建完成了。</h3><p>vue.png</p><h3 id="初始文件解析"><a href="#初始文件解析" class="headerlink" title="初始文件解析"></a>初始文件解析</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">├── build                           // 编译配置文件</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── build.js</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── check-versions.js</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── utils.js</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── vue-loader.conf.js</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── webpack.base.conf.js</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── webpack.dev.conf.js</span><br><span class="line">│   └── webpack.prod.conf.js</span><br><span class="line">├── config                          // 项目基本设置文件夹</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── dev.env.js                  // 开发配置文件</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── index.js                    // 配置主文件</span><br><span class="line">│   └── prod.env.js                 // 编译配置文件</span><br><span class="line">├── node_modules                    // 项目依赖包文件夹</span><br><span class="line">├── src                             // 我们的项目的源码编写文件</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── assets                      // 初始项目资源目录</span><br><span class="line">│   │   └── logo.png</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── components                  // 组件目录</span><br><span class="line">│   │   └── HelloWorld.vue          // 测试组件</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── router                      // 路由配置文件夹</span><br><span class="line">│   │   └── index.js                // 路由配置文件</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── App.vue                     // APP入口文件</span><br><span class="line">│   └── main.js                     // 主配置文件</span><br><span class="line">├── static                          // 资源放置目录</span><br><span class="line">├── .babelrc</span><br><span class="line">├── .editorconfig</span><br><span class="line">├── .eslintignore</span><br><span class="line">├── .eslintrc.js                    // ESLint配置文件</span><br><span class="line">├── .gitignore</span><br><span class="line">├── .postcssrc.js</span><br><span class="line">├── index.html                      // 项目入口文件</span><br><span class="line">├── package.json                    // 项目依赖包配置文件</span><br><span class="line">├── package-lock.json               // npm5 新增文件，优化性能</span><br><span class="line">└── README.md                       // 项目说明文档</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="" alt="directory.png"></p><h3 id="根据自己需求重配src目录"><a href="#根据自己需求重配src目录" class="headerlink" title="根据自己需求重配src目录"></a>根据自己需求重配src目录</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">├── api                             // 接口调用工具文件夹</span><br><span class="line">│   └── index.js                    // 接口调用工具</span><br><span class="line">├── components                      // 组件文件夹，目前为空</span><br><span class="line">├── config                          // 项目配置文件夹</span><br><span class="line">│   └── index.js                    // 项目配置文件</span><br><span class="line">├── css                             // css 样式存放目录</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── base                        // 基础样式存放目录</span><br><span class="line">│   │   ├── _base.scss              // 基础样式文件</span><br><span class="line">│   │   ├── _reset.scss             // 浏览器初始化文件</span><br><span class="line">│   │   ├── _mixin.scss             // scss 混入文件</span><br><span class="line">│   │   └── _variables.scss         // 公共变量文件</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── layouts                     // 页面样式文件夹</span><br><span class="line">│   │   ├── _footer.scss</span><br><span class="line">│   │   └── _header.scss</span><br><span class="line">│   └── common.scss                 // 主样式文件</span><br><span class="line">├── img                             // 图片</span><br><span class="line">├── page                            // 我们的页面组件文件夹</span><br><span class="line">├── router                          // 路由配置文件夹</span><br><span class="line">│   └── index.js                    // 路由配置文件</span><br><span class="line">├── store                           // vuex</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── modules                     // vuex项目模块文件夹</span><br><span class="line">│   └── index.js                    // vuex主文件</span><br><span class="line">├── utils                           // 常用工具文件夹</span><br><span class="line">│   └── index.js                    // 常用工具文件</span><br><span class="line">├── App.vue                         // APP入口文件</span><br><span class="line">└── main.js                         // 主配置文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="配置-static"><a href="#配置-static" class="headerlink" title="配置 static"></a>配置 static</h3><p>文件如果是放在 src 目录里面，则每次打包的时候，都需要打包的。这回增加我们的打包项目的时间长度。而且，一些地方放的文件，我们一般是不会去修改的，也没必要 npm 安装，直接引用就好了。可以根据自己的情况，对这些可以不进行打包而直接引用的文件提炼出来，放在资源目录里面直接调用，这样会大大的提高我们的项目的打包效率。<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">├── css             // 放一些第三方的样式文件</span><br><span class="line">├── font            // 放字体图标文件</span><br><span class="line">├── image           // 放图片文件，如果是复杂项目，可以在这里面再分门别类</span><br><span class="line">└── js              // 放一些第三方的JS文件，如 jquery</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;简单记录一下vue-cli构建项目，真的简单记录。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;安装&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#安装&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;安装&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;安装&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight plain&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;# 全局安装 vue-cli&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;$ npm install --global vue-cli&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;# 创建一个基于 webpack 模板的新项目&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;$ vue init webpack my-project&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;# 安装依赖，走你&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;$ cd my-project&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;$ npm run dev&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
    
